{
  "stem": "4189.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And those people that were working there with those striped uniforms, they were taking all those suitcases and were lining them up and putting them away.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were trying to whisper to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were saying, walk, walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In the beginning we couldn't figure out, what were they trying to tell us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Walk But soon we found out what they were trying to tell us, because the SS that were there that separated all of those people, they said look, you are here in Auschwitz now.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This is a labor camp, and you're going to work here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And everybody that can work will get food and will get lodging and will be taken care of.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, anybody that feels that he cannot walk now should step to the other side because the camp is about 10 minutes march away from here.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And those people that cannot walk or are tired, there will be trucks that will take them to the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now we realized what they were telling us, those people with the pajama uniforms.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were telling us to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we, of course, most of us from-- that came from France, we walked, marched to the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we found out that those people that could not walk, they never went to the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They went straight to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were all killed immediately.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, when we arrived in Auschwitz in the, in the camp and the gate, when we arrived by the gate, in front of the gate, we saw this huge sign over the gate.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it said, [NON-ENGLISH], work gives freedom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all this, of course, put us in deep shock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We, we from one moment to the next, they hit us with all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
